{"tid":1795702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尖沙嘴鐘樓噴黑字傷人 裝修判頭囚四月","createTime":"2019-12-24T06:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:26:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb60a37f455e25760b08c2f12a52bdff895f836","tid":1795702,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:12:50.000Z","msg":"34歲裝修判頭聲稱在8月初受政見不同人士挑釁，心生不忿下，在尖沙嘴梳士巴利道鐘樓，以黑漆噴上「五十不變 一派胡言」、「百年基業 毀於林鄭」字句，期間將介入的途人打傷。涉案判頭早前承認刑事損壞罪及對他人身體加以嚴重傷害兩罪，裁判官今於九龍城裁判法院直言，不能以暴力宣洩對政見的不滿，但考慮到其有悔意及願意賠償，共判囚4個月。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀判刑指，被告黎偉邦（34歲）累積的情緒與現時有關，但拒絕接受以暴力解決問題。嚴官又指，鐘樓為法定古蹟，屬大眾擁有而有價值的建築物。事件中，事主勸止不果繼而受襲，致其右手骨折，手腳皆有傷痕，考慮到黎願意賠償、有悔意，故就刑毀罪判囚2個月，傷人罪判監4個月，同期執行。控方透露事主或會提出民事索償。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FP_wz76F8CCt8bULbcZBtQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191224a123408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFP_wz76F8CCt8bULbcZBtQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191224a123408.jpg&h=155accc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E9%90%98%E6%A8%93%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91%E5%AD%97%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%88%A4%E9%A0%AD%E5%9B%9A%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88-043300590.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2598%25B4%25E9%2590%2598%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%2588%25A4%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%259C%2588-043300590.html&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlplm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=13b3b44b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E9%90%98%E6%A8%93%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91%E5%AD%97%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%88%A4%E9%A0%AD%E5%9B%9A%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88-043300590.html</a>"},{"pid":"316d036fa29b7eca2e275cddde1ac7731d21abf0","tid":1795702,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"之前連登仔話要同佢割"},{"pid":"9c9cb150e6fb823d2121ad64dca714f6afd0b63b","tid":1795702,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"想問𠝹刀呀叔量刑起點幾多個月?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19f8ec4a37f7248ad09ae10e491fd561ba35dcc","tid":1795702,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"幾好文采"}]}